parameters:
\F[sion_trouble]Shion: "Really...? You received a consultation from that
Shikura-san...?"

\F[sion_trouble]Shion: "Washio-sensei is coming on to you sexually? You hate
him... what?"

\F[sion_trouble]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "Ye-yes... Even though she's always so
incoherent... she was very clear..."

\F[sion_trouble]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[1]Shion: "This smells like a case... We can't just ignore
it..."

\F[sion_smile]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[1]Shion: "To have such a serious consultation, you must have
been close, Takamoto-sensei."

\F[sion_smile]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[2]Tsubaki: "No... For some reason, she's taken a liking to
me..."

\F[sion_smile]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[1]Shion: "Well then, let's go together and confirm the facts
with Washio-sensei. There could be a misunderstanding after
all."

\F[sion_smile]\FF[tubaki_trouble]\AA[1]Shion: "Anyone would be. To be accused of sexual harassment,
and no one doubts it... That's the kind of person he is."
